caption.title: Phylogenetic tree of DENV-1 isolates.
caption.p: The two sections to the right show enlarged images of the lower left boxes containing the Nepal sequences from the present study. Sequences are labeled by accession number, country, year of isolation, and genotype. Tree is labelled with posterior probability at node. Detail tree with all of the sequences used for genotyping is shown in S1 Fig. Constructed using BEAST v2.5.1 with Gamma+I+T93 substitution modeled against the DENV genotyping database.
